text: No Culture is the sixth album by Vancouver-based indie rock band Mother Mother, released on February 10, 2017. It was produced by Ryan Guldemond, Brian Howes and Jason Van Poederooyen. == Track listing == ==Personnel== *Molly Guldemond – vocals and keyboard *Ryan Guldemond – guitar and vocals *Jasmin Parkin – keyboard and vocals *Ali Siadat – drums *Mike Young – bass ==Charts== {| class="wikitable sortable plainrowheaders" style="text- align:center" |- ! scope="col"| Chart (2017) ! scope="col"| Peak position |- |} ==References== Category:Mother Mother albums Category:2017 albums
